What is FIGlet?

FIGlet is a program for making large letters out of ordinary text 

 _ _ _          _   _     _     
| (_) | _____  | |_| |__ (_)___ 
| | | |/ / _ \ | __| '_ \| / __|
| | |   <  __/ | |_| | | | \__ \
|_|_|_|\_\___|  \__|_| |_|_|___/

This one also includes all contributed fonts including these from
banner(6), the ms-dos and international (and CJK) fonts.
